        "subject": "LU-19856 ldiskfs: restore commit info on ldiskfs patches",
        "message": "LU-19856 ldiskfs: restore commit info on ldiskfs patches\n\nAdd and improve the provenance of ldiskfs patches that have\nbeen ported to new kernels, but lost the original commit\ninformation (LU ticket, Author, Change-Id, Reviewed-by, etc).\n\nThis is useful for understanding why each patch exists, and\nproviding references to find out more about the background.\nIt will also be useful when patches are submitted upstream.\n\nIn some cases this was partially available, but make it\nmore consistent between patches for ease of reference.\n\nThis information should be preserved when patches are\ncopied while porting to new kernels.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I427eb558dd0ae4ed81de2bca5ff3edd4e4a427c5\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/63825\nTested-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
